L["encounter:45412"] = "Unholy Aura ticks shadow dmg each second, it is just possible to get out of range of this. He will also spawn skeletons which he can destroy to heal himself.\n\nAoE the Skeletons as soon as possible, you can use Strat Holy water for this." -- Lord Aurius Rivendare in Stratholme
L["encounter:10435"] = "Tank & Spank. Boss does a big aggro-wiping knockback with Mighty Blow so best to tank with your back against a wall, will also use Crowd Pummel to the party knocking them back and interrupting spellcasting for 4 seconds, he will Enrage the entire fight increasing his Damage and Attack speed which stacks 25 times" -- Magistrate Barthilas in Stratholme
