L["encounter:62346"] = "++SALYIS'S WARBAND (GALLEON)\n\nOne Tank on boss in close under head for Cannon Barrage. Others Tanks pick up adds.\n\nAdds are kill priority.\n\nBig heals on Fire Shot and Stomp."
