-- Oondasta 
L["encounter:69161"] = "++OONDASTA\n\nTANKS:\n\nAggro Tank gains Alpha Male and faces Boss away.\n\nOn Frill Blast, use magic defensive cooldown.\n\nOn Crush, use physical defensive cooldown and swap. Not tauntable. Aggro Tank stops attacking to drop aggro and Alpha Male.\n\nCASTERS:\n\nOn Piercing Roar, stop casting to avoid silence.\n\nALL:\n\nStay behind boss to avoid Frill Blast's frontal hemisphere.\n\nSpread to avoid chaining Spiritfire Beam." 
