L["encounter:71953"] = "++XUEN\n\nSpectral Swipe: Frontal cone. Tanks face boss away and swap on debuff drop.\n\nLeap: Move away.\n\nCrackling Lightning: Stay spread to avoid chaining.\n\nChi Barrage: Move away from impact location.\n\nAgility: Purge from Boss."
